Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.02,0:01:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,My old man...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.49,0:01:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,turned out to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.58,0:01:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why are you telling me this now?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.15,0:01:42.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I have become a participant for Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.99,0:01:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium? What now?\NWhat is this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.67,0:01:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a place where I fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.59,0:01:52.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This {\i1}fighting{\i0} too...\NWhat the hell is this all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.68,0:02:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, in this place, there's a\Nslotter under the name of Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.25,0:02:06.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This man is referred to as "Finger of God."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.85,0:02:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a man wielding a great technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.52,0:02:14.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My heart gets extremely agitated \Nfrom just watching Daiba press the buttons.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.46,0:02:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,So I want to fight Daiba myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.33,0:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I turn white ash, \NI want to burn hot and bright, fighting him!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.10,0:02:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.04,0:02:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.10,0:02:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns out, you've been fighting \Nin some place I never heard of, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Me or Slothium - \Nwhich one is more important?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.97,0:02:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are...\NNot subject to comparison.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.35,0:02:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,All the parameters are different...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.90,0:02:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NBut I want an answer - what if you had to choose?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.77,0:02:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are important to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.30,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I care for Yuri more than for anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.26,0:02:51.56,Default,,0,0,0,,If so, don't go there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.58,0:03:27.56,Song,,0,0,0,,{\q2\fade(900,900)\c&HFFFFFF&\bord0\shad4\blur1\4c&H686B90&\b1\fnHitch Hike\fs65\pos(310,70)\3c&HD0BFA9&}Episode 21\N {\fs160}\N\N\N\NYozakura
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.34,0:03:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,But I was pretty sure, the deadline is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.41,0:03:39.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's the day after tomorrow, \Nbut I suddenly had other plans.{/have a little thing to do elsewhere}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.41,0:03:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't be lenient \Njust because you handed it in early!{/Only because of that, I'm not going to forgive major omissions/mishaps}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.78,0:03:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I never expected you to.{/I didn't have anything of the kind in mind}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.71,0:03:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Editor Hino.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that a rude thing to say to Ginya \Nbefore you ever read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.28,0:03:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Read first, \Ncomplain afterwards.{/First - read, then quibble/objection - to follow}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.98,0:03:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I get it, I get it! \NI'll make sure to read it too!{/I should get to reading that}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.53,0:04:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.60,0:04:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,for a quick word.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to Yuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.54,0:04:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,When I went to "Bronze{-Silk} Dream," I was told she returned to the countryside suddenly. It had me a little upset{/worried}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you two have a quarrel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.28,0:04:24.42,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not about a quarrel. Rather, just...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The question of the day is, \Ndo you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.89,0:04:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You do like her, don't you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.63,0:04:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's a piece of cake.{/nothing difficult} \NJust go ahead and be open about those feelings.{/tell her frankly about}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Go ahead \Nand be open?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.61,0:04:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright! Ginya, it's "OK!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This feels great!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.94,0:04:49.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm glad we took a detour!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.70,0:04:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Promise to fetch me tomorrow morning too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.08,0:04:54.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuri...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.25,0:05:15.77,Song,,0,0,0,,Kamoi Yuri
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.37,0:05:15.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Between me and Slothium,\Nwhich one is more important?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.77,0:05:19.73,Song,,0,0,0,,Missed calls{/Phone book}:\NOtonashi Ginya\N{Display}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.34,0:05:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}To me, both are important!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.14,0:05:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I know that my future lies with you.{this is new line he never said before so im unsure about /i1 it, also the meaning is a bit elusive, maybe it's "I will devote myself to yuri once the current thing is over/the importance of yuri spans into my future, unlike slothium"}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If so, don't go!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.55,0:05:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.68,0:05:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I care for you{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.21,0:05:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}sincerely and with all my heart!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.39,0:05:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But right now, \NI need to complete the conquest!{/want to finish the competition/conclude the showdown}{ditto as for prev line}{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.82,0:05:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Both are truly important to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.60,0:05:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, only today's battle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.21,0:06:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Come, Otonashi Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.65,0:06:10.61,Song,,0,0,0,,Bronze{-Silk} Dream
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.73,0:06:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Master's omelet rice is superb after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.40,0:06:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Master,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.62,0:06:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,no free service today?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just about{/thinking} to offer it{/put it out}.{methinks this wording was meant to imply "sorry, my thoughts were elsewhere/out of here" in addition to primary meaning, but I don't see a way to put propagate that to english}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.71,0:06:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.37,0:06:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,That's better!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.41,0:06:32.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A raw egg is consequently \Nthe superior source of raw strength.{/after all, the best way to become stronger is a raw egg}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm overflowing with strength!{/I'm full of power}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.55,0:06:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Save the demonstration of strength \Nfor the time of the battle.{this is highly unspecific, maybe "you need a source of power when you're about to join a fight"}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to tell me.{/I know [what I'm doing]}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.20,0:06:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Today, I'll make sure to win this{/certainly win}.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Good bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.59,0:07:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Ginya...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.80,0:07:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Slothium...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.64,0:07:32.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All the fights until now... Everything was for today. \NFor this one today's fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.81,0:07:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Something I have been yearning for.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.20,0:07:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.42,0:07:45.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's against you, \NI know this would be the fight of my life.{/I know I won't be disappointed with my ultimate/final fight ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.13,0:07:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Confrontation{/battle} of the century.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.97,0:07:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I{it sounds a little like bokura - "we" but that makes much less sense, since he'll be the only one allowed inside the arena}'ll get to witness it in detail{unsure maybe "make sure to"} \Nwith my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.10,0:08:08.06,Song,,0,0,0,,Challenger's Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.04,0:08:17.01,Song,,0,0,0,,King's Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,In a few minutes, we are starting the match between \Nthe King Daiba Ryo and the General Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.43,0:08:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Like it or not,{added} the King Daiba always wins.{half-guess, this sounds rather like "in a long lifetime, Daiba is king"}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.10,0:08:38.67,Song,,0,0,0,,The rules are: starting score - 50 coins.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.11,0:08:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't know what you're talking about! \NThe challenger Otonashi has a huge momentum{/is full of young vigor}.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.67,0:08:44.90,Song,,0,0,0,,{Absolutely no clue in the first part, kinda sounds like "3 days are in the 10th rounds", would make up my own rules}Upon the expiry of 12-hours time limit, \Nthe player with the highest score will be declared winner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:45.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Momentum alone \Nis not enough to surmount{this kanawai part is enigma to me, had to guess here} God's Finger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.62,0:08:49.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Barely made it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.41,0:08:51.47,Song,,0,0,0,,Challenger's Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.45,0:08:54.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.29,0:08:57.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.91,0:09:02.39,Song,,0,0,0,,King's Waiting Room
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.87,0:09:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't mind, could you go ahead?\NI'll catch up with you soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.14,0:09:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,As you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.68,0:09:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.72,0:09:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I could,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.52,0:09:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd feast my eyes forever \N{like this }on your sweet face.{added}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,But now, it's elsewhere where I have to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.48,0:09:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.95,0:09:52.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I am truly grateful for all you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.49,0:10:02.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.13,0:10:09.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenger's entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.80,0:10:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenger - Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.90,0:10:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Records:{/Wins and losses} 19 matches, 18 wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, on the streak \Nof 15 consecutive wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.62,0:10:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The King challenger's path of just 18 victories \Nis the shortest one in the history of Slothium.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I'll show you all a truly ultimate match.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.18,0:10:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And now, time for King's entry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.93,0:10:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,King - Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Currently, on a streak of 32 consecutive \Nsuccessful title defenses, the Ultimate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You, people, are happy out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.45,0:10:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In a matter of minutes, \Nyou'll get to see a genuine battle of life and death.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.45,0:11:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet I'm the one even happier than you are, \Nfor I'll get to play a main role in that battle.{/am the one participating directly ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.58,0:11:08.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hail fellow well met,{he actually says you've finally come but that is so hackneyed at this point} Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,My long days of yearning \Nfor this moment are over.{/I've been looking forward to this day}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.13,0:11:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,At last, I get to fight in Slothium \Nwhile sharing the ring with you.{/at the same ring as you}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.67,0:11:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,My delight is limitless.{/I'm as happy as I can get - going for a more formal and bony approach here to accent his showy indifference, contrasting with his words}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.03,0:11:20.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Ditto{/same} for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.27,0:11:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You attention to the middle, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.76,0:11:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We are introducing the machine \Nthat'll be used for today's match.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.97,0:11:34.85,Default,,0,0,0,,This machine is the logical extension{added} \Nof an original{/ingenious}{it's "a rare/collector's/unique/nonserial item" but I don't seem to know a word eloquent enough} phantom design from 15 years ago -
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.85,0:11:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozakura Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.64,0:11:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozakura?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.13,0:11:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,By letting the same staff extend the development{/reassembling the same staff that .../develop it further}, \Nit has been given a modern installment -
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.59,0:11:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Yozakura Seven.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.69,0:11:48.34,Default,,0,0,0,,They unearthed Yozakura?{/Yozakura, then?/you say?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.70,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's original design.{/development}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.84,0:11:55.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The most appropriate{/suitable/perfect} machine for the cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.34,0:11:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,In addition, for this match only,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:01.92,Default,,0,0,0,,alongside Dealer{/butler}, \Na special attendee{/witness} will be present{/attend}.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.79,0:12:12.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Oumi here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.86,0:12:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Special attendee?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.86,0:12:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi, how come?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.60,0:12:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't help the urge of watching \Nthe showdown of the century from the best seat.{/I just wanted to see ... from up close and in person}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.14,0:12:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.64,0:12:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,If the owner permits it, \Nthere's nothing we can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.31,0:12:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I don't want you \Nto interfere with the course of battle.{/get in the way ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.91,0:12:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.85,0:12:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that why he did all that for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.39,0:12:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Fight with everything on the line. \NThrow your everything at me!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.57,0:12:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}If you excuse me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.12,0:12:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Still...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.64,0:13:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i0}Still, the moment the battle is over, if need be, \Nby brute force, I'll have you undergo the checkup!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.11,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Only after the battle is over. \NHope you remember that.{/Don't forget that}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.84,0:13:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor is a special attendee?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.86,0:13:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,The match is starting any minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The challenger should now choose a machine \Nand get seated.{/please ... and take a seat}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.56,0:14:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Match starts in 5 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.17,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,3... 2... 1...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.97,0:14:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Start.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.51,0:14:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me, Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.54,0:14:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I will, Daiba Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With a final challenger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.87,0:14:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And with Yozakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.20,0:14:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What more there is to wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.61,0:14:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Keep cool and keep going, Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.28,0:15:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel that I'm starting to understand now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.76,0:15:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The dad's idea behind Yozakura.{unsure, maybe "the magnitude of dad's feelings for yozakura"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The idea behind bestowing mom's name \Nupon this machine.{again unsure, maybe "in this machine, the pain of leaving mom lives"}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.68,0:15:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.04,0:15:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No doubt about it now -\Nthis is {\i1}our{\i0} Yozakura.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A spellbinding sakura whirlwind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.97,0:15:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It all resulted in a great machine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.67,0:15:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I knew you'd be rapt with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.98,0:15:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,That Yozakura...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.87,0:16:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Appearances{/Form/constitution} changed, \Nbut it's still your heritage.{it's unclear who he refers to  - gin or kojiro so I left it unspecified as well, lit: with the shape altered, it was inherited}{there's also a completely different possibility for translation, here's what deepl suggests: It was passed down from generation to generation in different forms - barely 1 generation of people passed, but chances are, 6 gens of machine went by, judging by "seven" in name, but then again, where are they and why is the first one still ghost machine}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.38,0:16:05.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Kojiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.67,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo, your reign as the Ultimate King{/your existance in Ultimate King's status} \Nends today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.93,0:16:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Only if you manage to beat me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.59,0:16:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I will be the one winning this. \NSo once I'm at your King's{/get to ... ass}...{Lit: you, from your king's [throne] - this would be ass-hard to connect with the next line while preserving distinctly annunciated "king" in this one, so a bit of deliberate mistranslation here}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.17,0:17:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Once I reach the Ultimate King's throne, \NI'm deposing you!{/Once I'm atop the Ultimate King's hill, I'm throwing you down/get to the ... dragging you down/Lit: ousting forcefully from your ... seat/pedestal}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.22,0:17:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry to disappoint, but this dream of yours \Nhas no chance of getting fulfilled.{/but even if such is your dream, this wish cannot be granted}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.62,0:17:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my own dream, \Nso I'll fulfill it with my own hands!{/Only I myself can see to the fulfillment of my own dreams}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.35,0:17:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Then it's my own{he didn't say jibun here but that just sounds cool in combo with prev line} duty \Nto prevent that from happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:17.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All this time, I have been fighting to topple{/overthrow/defeat} you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will stop the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.02,0:17:27.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling down{/Scattering} sakura, blooming sakura - \Nboth are exquisite{/beatuful}.{this is one of those lines I encounter all the more often in the later episodes that feel like the foreboding of some greater moral or idea, which eventually never comes so they are just left off standing there as unfinished sculptures, that even I am unable to somehow make more consistent with their surroundings, or smooth corners so it does not look so out of place like a bad translation}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.91,0:17:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,We are about to find out \Nwhich kind of sakura you are.{ditto as for the previous line. I'm tempted to write in some made up moral from myself just to make this look some sense, even if detached from the original line}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.40,0:17:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Unsheathed it! \NGod's Finger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.31,0:17:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it Renchan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.72,0:17:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get impatient,{/rush} Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.24,0:17:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.40,0:17:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Like hell I'm gonna lose!{genuinely no idea about this "tamaru" maybe it's "do I have to lose and shut up/be stopped?" or "hurry up and lose already"}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.20,0:17:58.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Both play with an immense determination.{/have incredible spirit}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.84,0:18:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,If this keeps up, he can...{it's actually vice versa: If they manage it, at this rate... but again, I lie to make it more consecutive with the next line}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.72,0:18:03.19,Default,,0,0,0,,He can win safely.{/At this rate, safely...}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.79,0:18:20.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Look at me!{/how do you like this?}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.26,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.26,0:18:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {exactly }the genuine life or death{added because I think I used that wording before iirc} fight \NI was longing for.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.04,0:18:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,They truly are on even grounds.{/a very close match} \NEven their timings for hitting Big are nearly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.17,0:18:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Up to this point, \NGinya has been fighting on par with this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.31,0:18:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, if all comes together with all,{/maybe, perhaps, by any chance - I think that's what he meant with this weird wording}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.15,0:18:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,he can really get to Daiba's...{[ass]}{/he can really [defeat] daiba}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I owe it to{/it was thanks to} everyone of them \Nthat I was able to come that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.85,0:19:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, the only appropriate answer
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.94,0:19:05.82,Default,,0,0,0,,would be winning this battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.54,0:19:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.48,0:19:14.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't consider losing an option either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.42,0:19:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I will thank you for bringing me up \Nall the way to this point, by defeating you!{/by defeating you, I will express my gratutude for raising me until now}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.92,0:19:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Stick to that conviction{/determination} until the very end.{/don't forget that spirit ...}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Come at me, Otonashi Ginya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.55,0:19:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Incredible... \NToo incredible, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.02,0:19:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At this point, doesn't matter which one wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.47,0:19:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Until the very final roll is played, \NI won't take my eyes off.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.14,0:19:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,So true!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.47,0:19:50.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Such match is not something you see every day.{/one hell of uncommon}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.22,0:20:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Not again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.71,0:20:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Return to normal now...{/Settle down}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.90,0:20:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.24,0:20:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I beg you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.44,0:20:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a minor seizure.{/Am I overthinking?}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.46,0:20:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryo...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.02,0:20:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I must be the only winner!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Daiba Ryo.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Murasame Aoi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.01,0:22:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oumi Shunichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:42.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Otonashi Ginya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.98,0:22:45.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time:
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.14,0:22:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Incandescence{/Red-hot/scorching heat}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.12,0:22:49.79,Default,,0,0,0,,My finger will stop the time.
